<button id="printLabel" name="printLabel" style="color: #FFFFFF; background-color: #00487A !important; border-color: #00487A !important;">Print Label</button>

<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        
        $('[name=printLabel]').on('click', function() {
            var checked = $('[name=d-6514584-checkbox_id]:checked');

            checked.each(function(){
                var idQr = $(this).closest('tr').find('.column_id').text();
                var namaSkuVal = $(this).closest('tr').find('.column_nama_sku').text();
                var idProduksi = $(this).closest('tr').find('.column_id_produksi_botol').text();
                var isiPcs = $(this).closest('tr').find('.column_isi_per_ball_produksi').text();
                var shift = $(this).closest('tr').find('.column_shift').text();
                var pegawai = $(this).closest('tr').find('.column_employee').text();
                var tanggal = $(this).closest('tr').find('.column_tanggalMasukGudang').text();
                console.log(idQr);
                console.log(namaSkuVal);
                console.log(idProduksi);
                console.log(isiPcs);
                console.log(shift);
                console.log(pegawai);
                console.log(tanggal);
            })  
        });
    });
</script>
